    <section name="Operation">
      <p>The Transport Service tool operates as a standalone web application on a Tomcat server.  
      Typically, it is invoked from hyperlinks that are embedded in the results returned by the Search Service, 
      which may be running within the same Tomcat server or on a different server and host.
      <br/>
      The following topics will be covered below:
